nsubj(here, Muller)
aux(here, would)
advmod(here, not)
cop(here, be)
ccomp(hoped, here)
punct(here, ,)
mark(scheduled, that)
det(attempt, the)
nsubj:pass(scheduled, attempt)
aux(scheduled, would)
aux:pass(scheduled, be)
parataxis(here, scheduled)
case(somewhere, for)
obl(scheduled, somewhere)
case(control, beyond)
nmod:poss(control, Hoag)
case(Hoag, 's)
obl(scheduled, control)
punct(realized, .)
